title: Rudimentary Peni - Death Church - 1983 (320kbps CBR - INCREASED
description:
Rudimentary Peni's classic album "Death Church" (1983), in 320kbps CBR, and volume increased by 7.5dB to bring it in line with more modern recordings (so you can add songs to your party playlists without having to constantly dive for the volume knob!).

Rudimentary Peni were part of the British *Anarcho-Punk* movement (as it's now known), but were VERY STRANGE, almost surrealistic, and their unique music has now been adopted by those into *Death Rock*.

Included are the artwork (with the cover as *cover.jpg*, so most media players will load it) and lyrics. Enjoy!
